        "text": "Long-term risks: tenant damage, non-payment eviction (6-12 months), no owner flexibility. Airbnb risks: seasonal income fluctuation, regulation changes, management effort. Professional management mitigates most Airbnb risks through guest screening, damage deposits, and consistent quality."
